{"tid":917244,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"奧斯卡大導演貝托魯奇逝世享年77歲　曾執導《末代皇帝溥儀》","createTime":"2018-11-26T09:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T02:53:09.000Z","uid":83713,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3463bcf9e99dd9f008adc4b5e7c8984b87d300","tid":917244,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:31:07.000Z","msg":"意大利知名編劇及電影導演貝托魯奇（Bernardo Bertolucci）逝世，享年77歲。<br />\n<br />\n他憑電影《末代皇帝溥儀》獲得奧斯卡金像獎最佳導演、英國影視藝術文化學院電影頒獎禮（BAFTA）最佳影片、金球獎最佳導演等多個獎項。他在2011年第64屆康城電影節上獲頒榮譽金棕櫚&mdash;終身成就獎。<br />\n<br />\n他在1987年執導傳記片《末代皇帝溥儀》，它是史上第一部獲准進入北京紫禁城實景拍攝的電影。<br />\n<br />\n貝托魯奇也憑借執導的愛情片《巴黎最後的探戈》（Last Tango in Paris）獲得第46屆奧斯卡金像獎最佳導演提名。<br />\n<br />\n出身自意大利北部小鎮帕爾馬的貝托魯奇之前已卧病在床。路透社引述媒體報道，他在羅馬的家中去世。"},{"pid":"e61c7208b7be968a8f5b4f66fcc6ef759d8aa639","tid":917244,"uid":69696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:40:19.000Z","msg":"Last Tango in Paris令我深深明白到咩係唯美、節奏慢、有濃厚歐洲氣息嘅歐洲電影"},{"pid":"b8e5218439c84bb9ff041325de8bc205fbeb96a2","tid":917244,"uid":7363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"一路好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MI5DyZXcHVI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMI5DyZXcHVI&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=671d54d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MI5DyZXcHVI</a>"},{"pid":"3d7d7472e68ecb86c79937449b0772bb81d0cbc2","tid":917244,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8e5218439c84bb9ff041325de8bc205fbeb96a2","tid":917244,"uid":7363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"一路好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MI5DyZXcHVI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMI5DyZXcHVI&d=6cKArv8XvmPo8OEjbone%2FZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=671d54d2\" data-auto-